code: @Test public void testMixedCase() throws Exception {     String out = template.requestBody("netty4-http:http://localhost:{{port}}/Shopping", "Camel", String.class).     assertEquals("Bye Camel", out).     out = template.requestBody("netty4-http:http://localhost:{{port}}/shopping", "World", String.class).     assertEquals("Bye World", out). }
